.poolside/

codedb.snapshot
# Added by code-review-graph
.code-review-graph/

# Local-only Go workspace files
go.work
go.work.sum

# LanceDB native artifacts (downloaded by scripts/lancedb-install.sh).
# Binary blob per-platform — don't commit. See
# internal/rag/doc/SPIKE_RESULT.md for the provisioning flow.
.lancedb-native/

# --- Rust ---
# Cargo build artifacts from services/rag-engine/. We commit Cargo.lock
# at the workspace root (it IS a binary crate) but ignore the target/
# cache. `Cargo.lock` files inside member crates are redundant — cargo
# workspaces write a single lock at the workspace root.
services/rag-engine/target/
services/rag-engine/**/target/
apps/web/.mcp.json

# pnpm workspace cache (worktree artefact)
node_modules/.pnpm-workspace-state-v1.json

# macOS folder metadata
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store

# codedb local index snapshot (generated)
codedb.snapshot
**/codedb.snapshot

# Imported sandbox workspaces
sandboxes/cloud-agents/target/
sandboxes/cloud-agents/.lsp-servers/
sandboxes/cloud-agents/.bridge-attachments/
sandboxes/employee/target/
sandboxes/employee/logs/
sandboxes/employee/workspace/
sandboxes/employee/openrouter-proxy/conversations/
